OL,3,CThe Devon charity tackling addiction
OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,FA charity in Devon which uses sport to
OL,7,Fsupport people through addiction
OL,8,Frecovery hopes to grow across the
OL,9,Fcountry after becoming a registered
OL,10,Fcharity.
OL,12,FConnor Shannon started the Addicts to
OL,13,FAthletes group after overcoming a
OL,14,Fdecade of substance abuse by using
OL,15,Fexercise as part of his recovery.
OL,17,FHe documented his training for
OL,18,FParkruns, marathons and triathlons on
OL,19,Fhis YouTube channel.
