OL,3,CThe Devon charity tackling addiction
OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,F"People were leaving comments saying
OL,7,Fthey'd been in a similar situation,
OL,8,Fand that was where the idea of Addicts
OL,9,Fto Athletes started," he said.
OL,11,F"I just got that idea that, if it's
OL,12,Fhelping me, it can help other people."
OL,14,FConnor and his volunteers run a wide
OL,15,Frange of activities for people
OL,16,Fexperiencing addiction, from weekly
OL,17,Fcycles and running sessions to open-
OL,18,Fwater swimming, coasteering and golf.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G2/9
