OL,3,CThe Devon charity tackling addiction
OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,F"Part of it is kind of selfish, it
OL,7,Fkeeps me sober as well at the end of
OL,8,Fthe day. It's great to see everyone
OL,9,Fflourishing and getting something out
OL,10,Fof the activities."
OL,12,FThe number of people accessing drug
OL,13,Fand alcohol treatment services in
OL,14,FDevon and Cornwall has increased in
OL,15,Frecent years, according to Office for
OL,16,FNational Statistics data.
