OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,FThere was a 7% rise in adults using
OL,7,Fthese services across the UK in 2023-
OL,8,F24, the largest rise in a single year
OL,9,Fin more than a decade, according to
OL,10,Flatest government figures.
OL,12,FHowever, addictions come in many forms
OL,13,Fand statistics do not reflect all of
OL,14,Fthose who are not getting support.
OL,16,FService user Ivi said there is a
OL,17,F"camaraderie" between people who
OL,18,Fattend the sessions, no matter their
OL,19,Fpersonal experiences.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G5/9
