OL,3,CThe Devon charity tackling addiction
OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,F"It doesn't really matter whether any
OL,7,Fof these guys have an addiction to
OL,8,Fgambling, porn, shopping, street drugs
OL,9,For alcohol - there's more similarities
OL,10,Fthan there are differences. We meet
OL,11,Fpeople and instantly feel a
OL,12,Fcamaraderie, people know where we've
OL,13,Fcome from," he said.
OL,15,F"I've had my problems along the way,
OL,16,Fand people have been around to help
OL,17,Fpick me up. I see people who come in
OL,18,Fwho are where I was maybe six months
OL,19,Fago. We take care of each other."
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G6/9
