OL,3,CThe Devon charity tackling addiction
OL,4,Cthrough exercise
OL,6,F"It's good to see people go from
OL,7,Fhaving big bags under their eyes,
OL,8,Flooking grey, to actually having
OL,9,Fcolour back in their face and looking
OL,10,Fforward to life."
OL,12,FAddicts to Athletes currently supports
OL,13,Fpeople in North Devon, but volunteers
OL,14,Fthere hope to spread their work
OL,15,Ffurther.
OL,17,F"Addiction doesn't discriminate, it's
OL,18,Fin every area, every aspect of life,
OL,19,Fany age," said Connor.
